OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBan water bosses' bonuses  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fnow, say campaigners       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Water company executives should        
OL,6, immediately lose their bonuses if the  
OL,7, firm they run causes environmental     
OL,8, damage, such as illegal sewage spills  
OL,9, into rivers, campaigners say.          
OL,11,FRegulator Ofwat is to consult later    
OL,12,Fthis year on whether plans to ban      
OL,13,Fbonuses could be introduced.           
OL,15,FEnvironment secretary Stephen Barclay  
OL,16,Fsaid it was time water company bosses  
OL,17,F"took responsibility".                 
OL,19,FBut a campaign group said the policy   
OL,20,Fshould be implemented immediately.     
